feedback.title: Birthday Party Feedback
feedback.body: The event was well organized and enjoyable. Music volume could be slightly lower.

feedback.title: Gym Workout Review
feedback.body: The workout session was intense and productive. Trainer guidance was excellent.

feedback.title: Website UI Suggestion
feedback.body: The color scheme is good, but the navbar should be more mobile responsive. Try adding a hamburger menu.

feedback.title: Bug Report - Form Validation
feedback.body: The login form accepts empty passwords. Please add proper validation.

feedback.title: Feature Request - Dark Mode
feedback.body: A dark mode option would improve visual comfort during night usage.
